Package com.skobbler.ngx.navigation

Contains classes needed for making a turn by turn navigation.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
SKNavigationListener Listener for the callbacks related to navigation received from the ngx map library
 

Class Summary
SKAdvisorSettings Stores information about the audio advisor settings, that will be used during a navigation.
SKCrossingDescriptor Class that contains information about how to generate visual advice images.
SKNavigationManager Class which handles all the navigation methods.
SKNavigationSettings SKNavigationSettings defines settings for turn by turn navigation.
SKNavigationState Class used in navigation for updating the route state.
SKVisualAdviceColor The SKVisualAdviceColor is used to store the colors of a generated visual advice image.
SKZoomLevelConfiguration SKZoomLevelConfiguration stores information about the speed interval for a zoom level that will be used during navigation.
 

Enum Summary
SKAdvisorSettings.SKAdvisorLanguage Languages supported by the advisor.
SKAdvisorSettings.SKAdvisorType Type of audio advisor.
SKNavigationSettings.SKNavigationMode Defines types of navigation.
SKNavigationSettings.SKNavigationType Navigation types
SKNavigationState.SKStreetType Specifies type of street.
 

Package com.skobbler.ngx.navigation Description

Contains classes needed for making a turn by turn navigation.
